metadata.name: Prince Ashoka's Crown
metadata.description: Prince Ashoka's Crown, a testament to regal magnificence, emanates a radiant splendor that befits his noble lineage. Forged from resplendent gold, its intricate design weaves together elements of grace and power. Adorned with vivid emeralds that sparkle like fragments of a lush forest, they mirror the verdant majesty of his kingdom. Rising from the crown's apex, proud and resolute, are the elegant horns, a symbol of strength and wisdom. As Prince Ashoka wears this crown, he exudes an aura of regal authority, his every step echoing the legacy of his ancestors, guiding his kingdom towards a prosperous and harmonious future.
